The coupon on the 70 mln dlr equitywarrant eurobond for Best Denki Co Ltd has been set at threepct compared with the indicated 3-1/8 pct, lead manager NikkoSecurities Co (Europe) Ltd said.    The exercise price was set 1,640 yen per share,representing a premium of 2-1/2 pct over today's closing priceof 1,600 yen. The foreign exchange rate was set at 154.40 yento the U.S. Dollar.    The five-year deal is priced at par. REUTER&#3;